Title: mk_logwatch: logwatch.d files were only loaded if logwatch.cfg was in place
Level: 1
Component: checks
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Edition: cre
State: unknown
Version: 1.5.0b8
Date: 1530535554

If no MK_CONFDIR/logwatch.cfg exists all configuration files below MK_CONFDIR/logwatch.d were ignored.
